product_name: Himalayan Dog Chew Yaky Yam Strength Dog Treats - 4 oz.
long_description: Himalayan Dog Chew Yaky Yam Strength dog treats have protein to supplement your canine companion's diet, helping build muscle in all dogs and produce milk in females nursing a litter. Specially formulated to appeal to a dog's primary senses: smoked cheese for smell and sweet potato for taste. All-natural ingredients also include yak milk, cow milk, brown rice flour, chicken powder and broth, lime juice and salt.
